<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Epithet" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Epithet,</orth> term, expression, phrase: <cit><quote>suffer love! a good e.!</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.2.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 2, 67</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the --s are sweetly varied,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 2, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a most singular and choice e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>they will not answer to that e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 170</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>horribly stuffed with --s of war,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 14</bibl></cit>.
